import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-listings', templateUrl: './listings.component.html', styleUrls: ['./listings.component.css'] }) export class ListingsComponent { public carListings: CarListing[] = []; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + 'api/carlisting/all').subscribe(result => { this.carListings = result; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface CarListing { id: number; year: string; make: string; model: string; comments: string; driveAwayPrice?: number; excludingGovernmentCharges?: number; nonDealerDetails?: { name: string; contactNumber: string; } dealerDetails?: { name: string; email: string; contactNumber: string; abn: string; } }
